    "en": "The Messenger of Allah (may Allah bless him and his family) said: Whoever would love to be the noblest of people, let him fear Allah. Whoever would love to be the most God-fearing of people, let him rely upon Allah. Whoever would love to be the richest of people, let him have more trust in what is with Allah, Mighty and Majestic, than in what is in his own hand.",
